Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:35.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}遺失了開啟樂園的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:40.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}接受懲罰死去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:44.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}向著深夜的迷途
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:49.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}無法忍受的荊棘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:53.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}鬆開的鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:22:03.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}追尋著永遠被埋葬的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:12.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}請不要看這殘破的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.09,0:22:21.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}破裂的牽絆 黑色的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:31.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}請不要來這裡 這你未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:38.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}下著絕望的雨的世界……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:39.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}現在、完結
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:45.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}如火焰般閃耀於汝等心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:47.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}主宰汝等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:35.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}楽園の扉開く　鍵を　失くして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:40.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}罰を受けし心は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:44.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}夜の迷路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:49.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}茨の王　赦さず
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:53.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}解けめ鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:22:03.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}求めたのは　永遠　埋めたは愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:12.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}穢れ壊れた　僕をみないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.09,0:22:21.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}裂かれた絆　黒きレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:31.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}ここにこないで　君は知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:38.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}絶望の雨が降れる　世界が……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:39.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}今、終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:45.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}Which Shinetu as a flame in the midst of your palace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:47.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}And reigneth Amongst…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:59.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}月亮在輕輕低語
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:04.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}以誰也聽不到的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:08.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}不斷滿漲的潮水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:12.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}消失漸遠的記憶中的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:18.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}星星在密密記述著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}以誰也無法解讀的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:28.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}無限的語言的渦旋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:32.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}千億本書由此誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:40.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我的天空無限廣闊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:45.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}時間在飛速的鐫刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:50.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}毫無所知的虛無
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:54.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}匯聚的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:58.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}也只能在泥土中枯朽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:04.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即使如此我仍在呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:10.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}揚起晦澀難懂的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:15.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}至少將這聲音傳至天際
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:20.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}太陽也終會升起吧
